summary: This is a calendar entry for a canceled meeting titled 'Hold for Maxwell witness meetings' scheduled for April 29, 2021, involving personnel from the FBI, US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS), and NYPD. It indicates coordination for witness meetings related to the Ghislaine Maxwell case.

events.title: Canceled Maxwell Witness Meetings
events.description: A scheduled meeting titled 'Hold for Maxwell witness meetings' was canceled. The meeting was intended to involve personnel from the FBI, USANYS, and NYPD.

keyFacts: A witness meeting related to the Ghislaine Maxwell case was scheduled for April 29, 2021, but was canceled.
The meeting involved coordination between the FBI, the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS), and the NYPD.
The calendar entry was created on April 26, 2021, and modified on April 29, 2021, indicating last-minute changes to the schedule.
